        "text_GjcR9H": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Last updated: Dec 1, 2025</strong></p><p>At PallyWear, we are committed to delivering high-quality products and a smooth shopping experience. To ensure full transparency and fairness, please review our return and refund guidelines before placing an order.</p><h2><strong>1. Customized Products (Made-to-Order / Personalized Items)</strong></h2><p>Customized items are created specifically based on your design, text, logo, or personalization details. Because these products are produced uniquely for each customer, <strong>they are not eligible for return, exchange, or cancellation after printing or production begins</strong>.</p><h3><strong>Design Preview Guarantee (Full Refund Before Printing)</strong></h3><p>Before your customized product is printed, we will share a design preview (mock-up) for your approval.<br/><br/>If you are <strong>not satisfied with the preview</strong>, you may request a <strong>full refund</strong> before printing starts.</p><h3><strong>After Approval / Printing Begins</strong></h3><p>Once you approve the preview <strong>or</strong> printing begins, the order becomes <strong>non-returnable and non-refundable</strong>, as it has been personalized exclusively for you.</p><h3><strong>This applies to all customizations, including:</strong></h3><ul><li>Personalized text</li><li>Logo printing</li><li>Custom names or numbers</li><li>Custom artwork or design printing</li></ul><h2><strong>2. Non-Customized Products (Regular Clothing & Accessories)</strong></h2><p>We accept returns for non-customized products that are <strong>unused, unwashed, undamaged</strong>, and have all <strong>original tags and packaging intact</strong>.</p><h3><strong>Return Request Window</strong></h3><p>To ensure product quality and hygiene, return requests must be submitted <strong>within 24–48 hours of delivery</strong>, specifically for:</p><ul><li>Wrong item received</li><li>Wrong size/variant sent</li><li>Manufacturing defect</li><li>Quality issues (supported with photos/video)</li></ul><p>After 48 hours from delivery, non-customized items become <strong>ineligible for return</strong>.</p><h3><strong>Not Eligible for Return If:</strong></h3><ul><li>Product is used, washed, worn, or damaged</li><li>Tags or original packaging are missing</li><li>Perfume, deodorant, or usage marks are present</li><li>Product is older than 48 hours from delivery</li><li>Accessories show signs of use</li></ul><h2><strong>3. How to Request a Return</strong></h2><p>To request a return, please email <strong>info@pallywear.com</strong> with:</p><ul><li>Order number</li><li>Reason for return</li><li>Clear photos (and video if possible)</li><li>Unboxing video (recommended for faster approval)</li></ul><p>After review and approval, we will arrange a pickup within <strong>2–3 working days</strong>.</p><h2><strong>4. Refund Process</strong></h2><p>Once the returned item reaches our facility:</p><ol><li>The product will be inspected.</li><li>If approved, a <strong>refund will be issued to your original payment method</strong>.</li><li>A refund confirmation email will be sent to you.</li></ol><h3><strong>Refund Timeline</strong></h3><ul><li>Banks may take <strong>5–7 working days</strong> to reflect the amount.</li><li>Some credit/debit cards, UPI apps, and wallets may take <strong>up to 30 days</strong> depending on the issuer.</li></ul><h2><strong>5. Late or Missing Refunds</strong></h2><p>If your refund has not been received within the expected timeline:</p><ol><li>Re-check your bank account or UPI wallet.</li><li>Contact your card/UPI provider.</li><li>Contact your bank.</li><li>If still unresolved, email us at <strong>info@pallywear.com</strong> and we will assist you.</li></ol><h2><strong>6. Delivery Time</strong></h2><p>Orders are typically delivered within<strong> 3-7 business days</strong>.<br/><br/>Please note: Delays caused by courier partners, weather conditions, holidays, or customer unavailability are outside our control.</p><h2><strong>7. Tracking Information</strong></h2><p>Tracking details will be sent to your <strong>email</strong> or <strong>WhatsApp</strong> as soon as the order ships.</p><h2><strong>8. Incorrect Shipping Address</strong></h2><p>If you entered an incorrect address, please contact us immediately.<br/><br/>We will <strong>try our best</strong> to update it, but changes cannot be guaranteed once the order has been processed.<br/><br/>Orders delivered to an incorrect/incomplete address provided by the customer are <strong>not eligible for a refund</strong>.</p><h2><strong>9. Order Cancellation Policy</strong></h2><ul><li>Orders <strong>cannot be canceled</strong> once they are processed or dispatched.</li><li>If you request cancellation <strong>before processing</strong>, a <strong>15% cancellation fee</strong> applies to cover payment gateway and handling charges.</li></ul><h2><strong>10. Invalid Reasons for Refund/Cancellation</strong></h2><p>The following reasons are <strong>not valid</strong> for refund or cancellation:</p><ul><li>“I changed my mind.”</li><li>“I found it cheaper somewhere else.”</li><li>“I no longer want the product.”</li></ul><p>Placing an order creates a <strong>binding purchase agreement</strong>, and we prepare your order immediately to ensure fast delivery.</p><h2><strong>Need Help?</strong></h2><p>For returns, refunds, design preview concerns, or order support, please contact:<br/><br/>📧 <strong>info@pallywear.com<br/></strong>📍 Chennai, India</p>"
          }
        }
